      • sortItems

        public static void sortItems(java.util.List<ShoppinglistItem> items)
        Sorts ShoppinglistItem, according to what ShopGun have defined the order of a list should look be. This method does not update the objects (as in previous_id isn't updated automatically).

        There is no requirement to use this sorting method. This is only meant as a nice to have.

        Parameters:
        items - A List to sort
